326
00:22:36,830 --> 00:22:38,790
100,100,000, first call.

327
00:22:39,960 --> 00:22:41,000
100,100,000,

328
00:22:41,000 --> 00:22:41,590
second call.

329
00:22:45,520 --> 00:22:46,790
