408
00:28:10,590 --> 00:28:11,790
Without all of you,

409
00:28:13,630 --> 00:28:15,040
I wouldn't be who I am now.

410
00:28:21,440 --> 00:28:23,040
The main purpose of this auction

411
00:28:23,870 --> 00:28:25,830
