for the Kalpunia Mining District.

412
00:28:26,830 --> 00:28:29,070
We're already close
to our target amount.

413
00:28:30,040 --> 00:28:32,040
Though Fanlong Mining's share auction

414
00:28:32,070 --> 00:28:34,350
was forced to stop

415
00:28:34,480 --> 00:28:35,630
by some bad actors,

416
00:28:36,630 --> 00:28:37,590
it's okay.

417
00:28:41,070 --> 00:28:42,480
