509
00:35:32,270 --> 00:35:33,070
That's an understatement.

510
00:35:34,150 --> 00:35:35,270
Not really.

511
00:35:37,270 --> 00:35:38,070
By the way,

512
00:35:38,550 --> 00:35:40,590
